CANSACRIFICE

NAME
        CanSacrifice()

SYNOPSIS
        mixed CanSacrifice(object who, object what, string deus)

DESCRIPTION
        Checks the religion of "who" to determine if their religious affiliation permits their sacrifice here.

EXAMPLES
         

LOCATION
        /lib/chapel


